  <summary date="2021-08-27T14:05:09Z" status="Introduced in House">COVID-19 Data Transparency Act

This bill requires the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) to standardize reporting by government health departments of COVID-19 data, including information related to hospital admissions, testing, contact tracing, and transmission rates.

In addition, the CDC must publicly post and periodically update this information on its website with individually identifiable information excluded.</summary>
